  "text": [
    "The skin of sleep",
    "is thin. It will not hold.",
    "Its contents stumble out.",
    "A nub of bone",
    "lodged in earth",
    "at the bottom of a pit.",
    "A stranger staring",
    "down from the rim.",
    "The skin of sleep is thin.",
    "It cannot hold.",
    "Lost names spill out.",
    "Children engraved",
    "in ash. A sea of blood.",
    "Only you, tenderness,",
    "stillborn, beneath",
    "the skin of sleep."
  ],
  "title": "The Skin of Sleep",
  "year": ""
